1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:03,687
An export is a handoff, not just a download.

2
00:00:03,687 --> 00:00:07,694
Decide whether the next person needs to read the argument,

3
00:00:07,694 --> 00:00:11,701
inspect the codebook, reuse the project in another tool or

4
00:00:11,701 --> 00:00:13,304
see the visual structure.

5
00:00:13,704 --> 00:00:18,792
Open Export and choose the format by purpose.

6
00:00:18,792 --> 00:00:23,244
A canvas image is useful for slides.

7
00:00:23,244 --> 00:00:25,788
A report supports reading.

8
00:00:25,788 --> 00:00:28,332
Excel supports tabular review.

9
00:00:28,332 --> 00:00:32,784
QDPX supports exchange with compatible qualitative-analysis software.

10
00:00:33,184 --> 00:00:38,528
Before handing off a codebook, review names, definitions, hierarchy and examples.

11
00:00:38,528 --> 00:00:43,386
A list of labels without decision rules gives the next

12
00:00:43,386 --> 00:00:47,272
coder very little chance of applying them consistently.

13
00:00:47,672 --> 00:00:52,348
For a visual export, fit the relevant nodes into view

14
00:00:52,348 --> 00:00:54,686
and remove unnecessary empty space.

15
00:00:54,686 --> 00:00:59,362
Check the image at ordinary slide or document size; tiny

16
00:00:59,362 --> 00:01:02,168
transcript text is not useful evidence.

17
00:01:02,568 --> 00:01:08,053
The guide documents the current export choices and their intended use.

18
00:01:08,053 --> 00:01:13,040
Review it before a deadline, especially when another application, committee

19
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:16,032
or archive requires a specific format.

20
00:01:16,432 --> 00:01:19,674
Downloaded files are outside QualCanvas access controls.

21
00:01:19,674 --> 00:01:24,305
Store them in the approved location, limit onward sharing and

22
00:01:24,305 --> 00:01:28,936
apply the study's retention and deletion rules to every copy.

23
00:01:29,336 --> 00:01:34,216
Before exporting, confirm the purpose, choose the right format, test

24
00:01:34,216 --> 00:01:38,608
readability and send the file to an approved destination.

25
00:01:38,608 --> 00:01:42,512
That turns a download into a responsible handoff.
